data.description: Beautiful 5 bedrooms home in the wonderful community of Miramar. Entertainer's delight floor plan with breakfast nook, open kitchen and family room with formal living and dining space.  Large guest bedroom with private bath on main floor.  Huge Master bedroom upstairs with French doors and massive California custom closet. Central game room and three bedrooms with walk in closets on second floor.  The home boasts many upgrades...granite counter tops in kitchen, wood floors throughout downstairs.  Updated ceiling fans in family room and master bedroom. Bonus: Solar panels
